Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:36.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The three of us second years were safely elected to the student council
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,despite being in an election with Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:59.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was looking at Touko the moment the results were released.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:03.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko's purpose was to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Rosa Foetida en bouton! How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:36.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I plan to do my best to not let down the expectations others have of me.{edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:39.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But why did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see. Noriko-chan, you don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's means you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How about you come with me, Yumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't quite know why, but I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:15.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You don't need to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:19.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You don't want to know her reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:24.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How should I put this? That doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to toss her aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Does it seem that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:29.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:35.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for disturbing you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, apparently the newspaper wants a comment from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:49.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tsutako-san said she wants to take a commemorative photo of the three of us afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.02,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,"I'm not tossing her aside." {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.98,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,That's certainly what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko, you come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, it's all right if you don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's meet up at the Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I still feel a bit insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:20.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,if I accept Yumi-sama's words, Touko might be able to be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Chinese food for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What if one of us had lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:35.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We'd have a party to cheer you guys up, or a party to make Yoshino happy. {TLC for a better way to word this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We'd just change the name of the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:42.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll admit, I was quite nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:47.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, what are you planning to do about Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you leaving her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There must be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Her smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:14.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,didn't mean anything like "What's wrong?" or "It's all right." or even "Leave it to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:20.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it was a smile that contained a combination of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:26.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama suddenly feels distant somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:40.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi wasn't even able to get the "to" from Touko out of her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:48.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She must have been chasing after Touko that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When she returned, her expression was clearly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Sa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I should welcome you back too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You sprained your ankle while skiing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:28.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-san, Suguru-san brought back some rice cakes as a souvenir from his skiing trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's have some right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hold on. I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Those two are good kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-chan and Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi and Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:59.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,On the twelfth, Touko had an argument with her parents and ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No one told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I didn't really want to make a big deal out of it, so I kept it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:12.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So is there some kind of relationship between Touko running away and Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I found Touko at Yumi's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At Yumi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She didn't visit her because she was someone to depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She met Yuuki close to where Yumi's house is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I told you it was on the twelfth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I know it was on the twelfth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What I'm asking is whether it was before or after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, it was in the week of their break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:44.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This happened before Touko refused Yumi's rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi was worried about Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She probably was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Does your sudden spark of interest mean that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,something happened between Touko and Yumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Suguru-san, you're Touko's cousin after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about your own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But still, something like that happened between Yumi and Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm Yumi's older sister, I can't get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I haven't answered your question if something happened or not
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,while you were gone, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:35.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:39.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan ran as a candidate for the student council and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have no idea why she choose to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though Yumi-chan was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Suguru-san, do you like Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying something so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:08:58.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:09.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I should have just laughed and said\N "I love Yumi-chan because she's a nice girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to be misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I would've felt in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but I've come to understand a few things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:23.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In terms of mass, my love for you is much greater than my love for Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a different kind of love, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're just as smart as ever, Sa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who are you comparing me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We should go back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:42.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If we stay in here for too long, auntie will start to think strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You forgot to wash your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just what you expect from cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They're both so fastidious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:07.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here are the plans for this year's Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This year, we'll be having another Valentine's Day event,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:18.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so we would like to ask for the cooperation of the Yamayuri Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:22.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,of which Rosa Chinensis and Rosa Foetida have already agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:23.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to turn them down, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even so-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please look at the handouts in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the same thing as last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:45.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, even if it's the same event, we'll be powering it up this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Last year, Rosa Chinensis' card was the only one that wasn't found within the time limit, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:51.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:56.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's just too unfortunate to never have your card found, even though you went to the trouble of hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:01.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This year, in order to avoid that, we're planning to have a way in which the losers can play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How? Specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:08.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We're planning to give a chance to those who cannot attend on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A chance for those who can't participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:16.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Up until the day before the event, we'll have people write down the areas where they think a card could be hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and put it into a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:21.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, the box won't be opened until the event starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so there's no way that the location of the cards can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:31.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If a card isn't found, then the person who guesses the correct location will be given the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And if no one guesses the correct location of a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:38.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The plan is to have the winner be the person who guesses the closest location,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:44.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but how about we plan out the details little by little by including everyone's opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, if there are any questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,About the event logistics written here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:58.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It says: The boutons that will become Roses will be mingling with normal students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Crap. I forgot to fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:06.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You used the plan from last year to format this plan, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I read that part, but I ignored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:15.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san you're going to be a Rose again next year, and Noriko-chan is your bouton, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So which one of you is participating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But Noriko, you're a bouton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:33.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But won't you be Rosa Gigantea next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, it clearly says "bouton" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It also says "Rose."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:45.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This may sound irresponsible coming from the one who caused the confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but what is everyone else's opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Our opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I did it last year, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That kind of logic won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:57.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If we accept your reasoning now, Shimako,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan can do the same thing next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:07.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But there's no guarantee that Noriko will become the next Rosa Gigantea after the election next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then let me say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:14.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Isn't it odd in the first place to have someone take that kind of position in the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako, why don't you participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Does it matter if you do it two years in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako, you have a lot of fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Let's do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Or is there a reason why you wouldn't be able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:41.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't want to hide my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's just?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just want to find the card that Noriko hides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:10.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I heard about last year's event from my classmates Atsuko-san and Miyuki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and I thought, "I want to look for Onee-sama's card."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:20.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But just as I was about to give up because I'm a bouton this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,we started talking about either the bouton or next year's Rose participates, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought this was a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:37.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:42.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako, are you worried about who'll be the Rosa Gigantea after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:47.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No. I believe that Noriko will legitimately succeed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:51.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then show her the side of you that's cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:56.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since it'll be something she'll have to do next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:57.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:13.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Mami-san, if you're doing this again this year, does that mean you plan to do it again next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:16.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's a popular event, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.13,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so happy. {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san has it good, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:25.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If we didn't have to see our Onee-sama off, we could immediately focus on our younger sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:32.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, aren't you angry that our Onee-sama agreed to this without asking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:45.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Although it's a problem, I also don't think there's a reason to refuse just like Onee-sama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Last year, Mizuno Youko-sama had her dream fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:03.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She wanted the Rose Mansion to be a place where elegance would always remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to see another dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nana-chan will be applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san? You're spilling the tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, you're calm, aren't you? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not quite sure, but you're very calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you aren't sure, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:54.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Aside from Nana and myself, what do you plan to do about Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What I plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're not going to make her your soeur?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:06.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She has to agree to it first, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:10.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I seem calm, maybe it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,because there's no reason for me to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No need to rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Things like "I have to find a sister before Onee-sama graduates!" or
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"I have to make Touko-chan my sister!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:31.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Strangely, it's like I've lost any impatience I once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Was there any cause for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:39.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there was any specific cause, but if I had to say it, it was the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The election?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:46.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ever since, I've been thinking about how I want my relationship with Touko-chan to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've been satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if I act hastily, the answer won't reveal itself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, don't become an adult by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eh? I'm not one at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:09.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What are you worried about? You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.13,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:13.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then, they chased after Yumi-san, and it became a game of tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:18.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After diligently reporting the whole thing, the Lilian newspaper became really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:23.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,According to rumor, it not only swept the high school division, but the middle school division too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.61,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh right! I thought of something good! {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it might be a bit difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you can make it happen, you'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.49,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,What're you-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing for you to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:32.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Will you allow students from the middle school division to participate this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Last year, some sneaked in to take a look, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah, I certainly heard something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:50.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll ask the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, Yumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:01.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I told you not to leave me behind, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:04.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is about allowing the middle schoolers to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:17.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well, in terms of results, we managed to gain the teachers' approval through a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:22.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They're allowed to participate only through the guessing portion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:27.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And that's how it is. So what are you going to do, Yoshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell Nana-chan right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be hasty about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:42.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Plus, even though everyone's different, the same thing might be affecting us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Soeurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Going to the Rose Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:51.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hold on a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:21.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're always so helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:28.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Right now, the only ones here are Yumi-sama and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have something to talk to you about, Noriko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:40.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, I wouldn't mind if Shimako-san or Yoshino-san were to come in and overhear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What? Did you think it would be about Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:52.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:58.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nothing's really happened, so I don't really have anything to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But if there's anything you want to ask me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:06.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can give you a satisfying answer though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Something I want to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Something I want to ask Yumi-sama right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why do you leave Touko alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can I trust you when you say that you won't toss her aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:26.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you think of Touko losing the election?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:32.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll feel like handing Touko your rosary a second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:54.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:09.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The proposal to allow middle schoolers to participate in the event that Yumi-san proposed was accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:13.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but there were actually a number of students that had an illegal head start last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since the teachers from the middle school division caught them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:20.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,they're discussing how to crack down on this for this year's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:21.26,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama likes Touko. {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:28.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That was the one thing I wanted to hear most from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Mama sometimes sees bad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,While she has nightmares, she calls out with a strained voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:14.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Although I came running to her, I was scolded and told not to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:19.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The reason Mama sees such dreams is because of a baby she lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:22.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I pretend not to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.09,0:24:27.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my precious family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.09,0:24:29.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time: Keyhole to the Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:33.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When can the door to the heart be opened?
